      "name": "Generate boarding cards",
      "description": "Request boarding documents for the checked-in tickets. The Operations API proxies the request to the Delivery microservice, which retrieves each ticket from delivery.Ticket, filters to segments checked in for the supplied departure airport, and generates the BCBP string. Returns an array of boarding cards each containing the BCBP barcode string compliant with IATA Resolution 792.",
      "type": "positive",
      "apiCall": {
